# Embedded Libs — Do Not Modify

**Do not edit, refactor, or modify any files in embedded `Libs` folders.**

These are third-party libraries (LibStub, Ace3, LibCopyPaste, LibDBIcon, etc.) that are vendored/embedded as-is. Changes to them can break compatibility, cause merge conflicts when updating, and diverge from upstream. If a task would require modifying a Lib, implement the needed behavior in addon code instead, or note that the Lib would need to be updated externally.
